title: [FSX/P3D] IRIS Pro Series Christen Eagle v1.2
description:
This is the latest build of IRIS Pro Series Christen Eagle for you guys.

This new build includes a revised FDE, a brand new sound pack, a new model with glass display (Christen Eagle IG), addition of autopilot to the cockpit and some new skins to the package.

This was a freak aerobatic plane when released years ago; it still is one of the best (THE BEST IMHO) despite its aging graphics. The latest updates only makes it better.

Tested this in P3D v2, seems to be working OK, so an option for P3D v2 were added as well when patching & rebuilding the original v1.2 installer. However, NO warranty is provided for P3D v2 compatibility on your computer. Try this in P3D v2 at your own risk.

SEED & ENJOY!
